data.description: PRICE MODIFICATION! We have the pleasure to offer for sale a beautiful 3 beds 2 baths home located in the center of Port Charlotte. This home has HURRICANE RATED WINDOWS AND ENTRY DOORS. WOW! A new roof and air-con system were installed in 2020. A brand new fridge in 2022. Hot water heater in 2018. Public water and public sewer. The home has been freshly painted inside. Ready to move in.   As you enter the home through the elegant hurricane rated front door you are greeted with the spacious open living, dining and family room area. The size will amaze and impress you! All tiled for easy maintenance. The kitchen with brand new wood cabinets and granite countertops is ideally situated in the center.  A pass through from the kitchen to the family room makes serving snacks and refreshments a breeze. The master bedroom to the right side of the home has laminate flooring and a walk-in closet. The adjoining private bathroom is complete with double sinks and a tub/shower combination. The two guest bedrooms with newer laminate flooring are situated on the other side of the home. The split bedroom design along with the guest bath is ideal for a growing family, or overnight guests. As you view the home you will notice all walls have rounded corners which are a very nice quality touch.  From the French doors in the living area you step out onto the large 16’X15’ concrete patio. A great place for putting your outdoor furniture and BBQ, enjoy the sunshine of Florida. The shed in the backyard is powered, very handy for storing your garden tools or completing small projects etc.   You can park your car even a big size truck under the sturdy carport. The double width driveway has ample space to park a boat or additional vehicles.  This home has great location. Close to restaurants, schools, hospitals etc and only a short drive to many beautiful beaches. For a private and personal viewing please contact us.
